Savage yellped when more shots hit his body. He saw that more people 
had come to fight him. Too many. He couldn't win. But he could still 
extract some revenge. He may be dumb, but he could still see that 
this valley was a romantic place for the two original bots. He sucked 
in, and than let out a huge spray of fire towards the bots, but than 
he change directions and aimed it at the valley! The trees and 
everything started burning. He than flew away slowly, with battle 
wounds now catching up wiht him.
